name: DailyDinner
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: daily dinner
des: Daily Dinner will help you find a great dish for you to make for dinner. Whether you want chicken, pasta, beef, or pork. Daily dinner will give you a suggestion for you on what to make for dinner. Dish options are: chicken, beef, pork, pasta, seafood, potato, and vegetable. Simply say thank you after you receive the suggestion and it will close the application.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
